Package: formatpaste
Type: Package
Title: Remove Hard Line Breaks in Clipboard Then Paste
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xianghui Dong
Maintainer: Xianghui Dong <dracodoc@gmail.com>
Description: Remove unneeded hard line breaks of text in clipboard, like text
    copied from pdf, then paste into current cursor position. Also included a
    function to flip windows path separator in clipboard, so that path copied in
    windows can be used in R.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: stringr,
    rstudioapi
